  "description": "Architecture decision framework for choosing between OmniStudio and the standard Salesforce platform (Screen Flow, LWC, Apex) for guided UI and data orchestration use cases. Covers the license gate, the Dynamic Forms \u2192 Screen Flow \u2192 OmniStudio continuum, Standard Runtime vs Vlocity managed package migration debt, and team skill considerations. NOT for implementation. NOT for OmniScript development or FlexCard configuration.",
